Class PayEvent

java.lang.Object
general.Event
specific.PayEvent
public class PayEvent extends Event
Represents an event where a customer pays for their items at the checkout. From being ready to pay to actually completing their payment.

      public PayEvent(float time, MakeCustomer customer, StoreState state)

      Parameters:
